CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1773940276
OL,3,C'I thought I'd have to quit work':
OL,4,CCommunity fight 'two-tier' menopause
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FI was joined by co-founders of one of
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland's first menopause
OL,9,Fsupport groups, Menopause Together,
OL,10,FRoisin Hillman and Karen Pateman. They
OL,11,Fsay a general lack of conversation and
OL,12,Fknowledge about peri-menopause and
OL,13,Fmenopause meant that getting the right
OL,14,Fhelp is difficult for women.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1773940276
OL,3,C'I thought I'd have to quit work':
OL,4,CCommunity fight 'two-tier' menopause
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,F"That's our mission...to educate,
OL,8,Fempower and support them so they know
OL,9,Fhow to talk to their GPs, how they can
OL,10,Fexplain which symptoms they are going
OL,11,Fthrough and how they are affecting
OL,12,Fthem on a daily basis. That is
OL,13,Finconsistent across Northern Ireland
OL,14,Ffor a variety of reasons," Roisin says.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1773940276
OL,3,C'I thought I'd have to quit work':
OL,4,CCommunity fight 'two-tier' menopause
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FSuch are the complications in
OL,8,Faccessing the right support, it's
OL,9,Fgiven rise to the fear that a parallel
OL,10,Ftwin track system is manifesting
OL,11,Fitself, with those who can afford to
OL,12,Fgo private, doing so while others have
OL,13,Fto navigate the public system.
OL,15,F"It does give a two-tier system. Not
OL,16,Feveryone can do that and where we are
OL,17,Fis that we want people to be able to
OL,18,Fgo to their GP but funding is
OL,19,Fdifficult," Karen said.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1773940276
OL,3,C'I thought I'd have to quit work':
OL,4,CCommunity fight 'two-tier' menopause
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,F"It depends on what works for you but
OL,8,Fyou have to have a voice. You have to
OL,9,Fbe able to stand up for yourself. If
OL,10,Fyour GP is your pathway, be ready with
OL,11,Feverything that you need to tell
OL,12,Fthem," Karen added.
OL,14,FFor women, in their 40s or 50s, their
OL,15,Flives look far different to the
OL,16,Fgenerations of similar ages before
OL,17,Fthem. There are societal reasons for
OL,18,Faccessing the right help too.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1773940276
OL,3,C'I thought I'd have to quit work':
OL,4,CCommunity fight 'two-tier' menopause
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,F"We also need to remember that women
OL,8,Fare living far longer now than we've
OL,9,Fever lived and we want to be fit and
OL,10,Fwe want to be able to do things. On a
OL,11,Fpersonal level if I wasn't taking HRT,
OL,12,FI would not be able to work as there
OL,13,Fwas a point where I thought I was
OL,14,Fgoing to have to leave work. There are
OL,15,Ffinancial implications as well,"
OL,16,FRoisin said.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
