PN,44207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1773940276
OL,3,C'I thought I'd have to quit work':
OL,4,CCommunity fight 'two-tier' menopause
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FComing back to that theme of
OL,8,Fcommunity, Roisin and Karen believe
OL,9,Fthat they have created their own
OL,10,Fcommunity, their own space where women
OL,11,Fcan be open and share information.
OL,13,F"We need people at the grassroots.
OL,14,FThis is what it's all about. It's all
OL,15,Fabout community, getting that
OL,16,Fcommunity around you. Whether it's
OL,17,Fmenopause or anything, getting those
OL,18,Fpeople, having your tribe around you
OL,19,Fto empower and support you, that's the
OL,20,Fmain thing," Roisin.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
